movie.overview: After witnessing her parents’ murder as a child in Bogota, Cataleya Restrepo grows up to be a stone-cold assassin. She works for her uncle as a hitman by day, but her personal time is spent engaging in vigilante murders that she hopes will lead her to her ultimate target: the mobster responsible for her parents' death.
movie.title: Colombiana

results.overview: Beneath Anna Poliatova's striking beauty lies a secret that will unleash her indelible strength and skill to become one of the world's most feared government assassins.
results.title: Anna

results.overview: While watching from her train window, Nikki Collins witnesses a murder in a nearby building. When she alerts the police, they think she has read one too many mystery novels. She then enlists a popular mystery writer to help her solve the crime on her own, but her sleuthing attracts the attentions of suitors and killers.
results.title: Lady on a Train

results.overview: Nathan is thirteen years old boy. Driven by his new friend Malik, he prepares himself for a strange ritual to become a member of a teens gang.
results.title: Titan

results.overview: A fashion model witnesses the brutal assassination of an investigative journalist by the Ku Klux Klan while traveling to a small town to visit her sister.
results.title: Storm Warning

results.overview: A social worker tries to end juvenile crime by getting involved with a street gang.
results.title: Crime in the Streets

results.overview: In this short film, a small-town newspaper editor struggles with what to publish on his paper's front page.
results.title: Important News

results.overview: After an unfortunate incident causes him to leave the "family business" and move to Los Angeles, Vinny Pallazzo is living a quiet life. When his nephew, Anthony, moves in with him, Vinny slowly learns to live life to the fullest again. However, Anthony is young, and is living life in the fast lane. He brings out the demons from Vinny's past. Now Vinny must try to stop Anthony from making the same mistakes that changed his life forever.
results.title: Lookin' Italian

results.overview: A woman fights to convince the police that she witnessed a murder while looking out her bedroom window.
results.title: Witness to Murder

results.overview: When terrorists target a young girl who witnessed an assassination, a heroic taxi driver comes to the rescue.
results.title: Viswam

results.overview: After living separate lives, three men try to reset their former turf that is now infested with gangsters to its former glory.
results.title: Bar Legend

results.overview: Having seen the double murder of his parents, autistic youth Tim Warden is sent to therapy with controversial therapist Dr. Jake Rainer. Jake tries to probe the silent child about what he saw, but he gets more details about the Wardens' household dynamics from Tim's teenage sister, Sylvie. As he spends more time with the siblings, Jake learns that the Wardens' marriage was not as perfect as it seemed, and he uncovers other new details that might help solve the crime.
results.title: Silent Fall

results.overview: Set in the ghettos of Paris in 2010, an undercover cop and ex-thug try to infiltrate a gang in order to defuse a neutron bomb.
results.title: District B13

results.overview: A tale of an inner city drug dealer who turns away from crime to pursue his passion, rap music.
results.title: Get Rich or Die Tryin'

results.overview: After her beloved younger sister, Reina, is gang-raped, Leona files a lawsuit against the perpetrators, Fujita and others. However, the case is dismissed and instead she is sued for defamation. In order to avenge Reina, who has become a virtual invalid, Leona is reborn as a hitman.
results.title: The Killer Angel Revenge

results.overview: Veronica, the new girl in town, is lured into the woods by a group of senior boys looking to make her a victim. But the boys don't know that Veronica's been trained to handle herself in surprisingly lethal ways.
results.title: Final Girl

results.overview: Hamlet, Prince of Denmark, finds out that his uncle Claudius killed his father to obtain the throne, and plans revenge.
results.title: Hamlet

results.overview: Based on the true life experiences of poet Jimmy Santiago Baca, the film focuses on half-brothers Paco and Cruz, and their bi-racial cousin Miklo. It opens in 1972, as the three are members of an East L.A. gang known as the "Vatos Locos", and the story focuses on how a violent crime and the influence of narcotics alter their lives. Miklo is incarcerated and sent to San Quentin, where he makes a "home" for himself. Cruz becomes an exceptional artist, but a heroin addiction overcomes him with tragic results. Paco becomes a cop and an enemy to his "carnal", Miklo.
results.title: Bound by Honor

results.overview: A beautiful felon, sentenced to life in prison for the murder of a policeman, is given a second chance – as a secret political assassin controlled by the government.
results.title: Nikita

results.overview: Lyon Gaultier is a deserter in the Foreign Legion arriving in the USA entirely hard up. He finds his brother between life and death and his sister-in-law without the money needed to heal her husband and to maintain her child. To earn the money needed, Gaultier decides to take part in some very dangerous clandestine fights.
results.title: Lionheart

results.overview: Dominic Toretto is a Los Angeles street racer suspected of masterminding a series of big-rig hijackings. When undercover cop Brian O'Conner infiltrates Toretto's iconoclastic crew, he falls for Toretto's sister and must choose a side: the gang or the LAPD.
results.title: The Fast and the Furious
